---
const sizes = "(min-width: 768px) 360px, 260px";
---
<section class="py-16">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="relative rounded-3xl bg-[#FAF7F5] shadow-sm border border-black/5 p-8 md:p-10 overflow-hidden">
      <!-- soft accent blob -->
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -left-24 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-black/[.06] to-transparent blur-2xl -z-10"></div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 items-center gap-10">
        <!-- Image: crisp, responsive, compact -->
        <div class="md:col-span-5">
          <div class="relative inline-block">
            <div class="absolute -z-10 inset-0 translate-x-1 translate-y-1 rounded-2xl bg-black/5"></div>
            <picture>
              <source type="image/webp" srcset="/studio-hq-480.webp 480w, /studio-hq-768.webp 768w, /studio-hq-1024.webp 1024w" sizes={sizes} />
              <img
                src="/studio-hq-1024.jpg"
                alt="D‑Essence Wellness treatment room"
                class="block w-[260px] md:w-[360px] h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-lg ring-1 ring-black/10 object-cover object-center"
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
              />
            </picture>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="md:col-span-7">
          <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <div class="text-[11px] font-medium tracking-[0.2em] text-black/60">MED SPA IN NEW WINDSOR, NY</div>
            <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
              Reflect Your Best Self<br/>With Exceptional Medical Aesthetics
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-6 text-[15px] leading-7 text-black/80">
              At D‑Essence Wellness, we believe true beauty begins with confidence. Our medical aesthetic center at
              <strong>871 Blooming Grove Turnpike Suite 102, New Windsor, NY 12553</strong> offers a welcoming and
              professional environment designed to enhance your natural features and care for your skin with the highest standards.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-7 text-black/80">
              Our non‑surgical, minimally invasive treatments combine advanced technology and personalized protocols to deliver safe, natural results.
              From aesthetic injectables and full‑face rejuvenation to peels, regenerative therapies, and advanced skin care, we focus on your overall well‑being and transformative experiences.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-6 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <div class="rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-4">
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Advanced Injectables</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-black/60">Personalized approaches for subtle, refined results.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-4">
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Full‑Face Rejuvenation</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-black/60">Harmonized plans focusing on the face as a whole.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-4">
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Laser & Skin Technologies</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-black/60">Resurfacing and innovative treatments for skin health.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-4">
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Care by Certified Experts</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-black/60">A warm, professional experience from start to finish.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-8">
              <a href="/appointment" class="relative text-sm font-medium tracking-wide">
                <span class="pb-1 border-b border-black inline-block">Book a Consultation</span>
              </a>
              <a href="/services" class="text-sm text-black/70 hover:text-black underline underline-offset-4">View all services</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
